    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, as a Reaction to taking damage, you can conjure a thick coat of golden armor which can take brutal impacts absorbing some damage for you. </p><p>When you do, you gain 6 DR (damage reduction) vs all sources and immunity to chakra damage or chakra cost penalties until the beginning of your next turn. This increases to 10 at 11th and 14 at 18th levels. You can do this a number of times equal to your Wisdom Modifier per Short Rest</p>",
